{"tid":944973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"憂慮中國軍力提升　日本擬採購美製長程導彈","createTime":"2018-12-17T13:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T23:36:05.000Z","uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"983b6947846c768df1aca4afc43bd5e7d5b48a8d","tid":944973,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T13:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181217/large/1545042784_33ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181217%2Flarge%2F1545042784_33ce.jpg&h=19225b4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了應對中國軍事軍脅，日本政府可能考慮採購美製長程導彈。 資料圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n隨着近年中國在海空軍力及飛彈方面實力不斷提升，日本政府亦計劃採購長程導彈抗衡。有分析指，此舉反映日本可能改變一貫以防衞為主的角色。<br />\n日本時事通信社報道，中國在過去20年間國防預算增加了12倍，尤其中國正在研發可安裝在戰艦上、射程540公里的飛彈，反觀日本自衞艦隊現時擁有的飛彈射程僅100至200公里，明顯相形見絀。<br />\n有見及此，內閣會議明天擬訂防衞計劃大綱時，打算加入考慮購買美國製JASSM（Joint Air-to-Surface Standoff Missile，聯合空對地距外飛彈）的構思。JASSM射程約900公里，只要把目標位置輸入飛彈，從日本領空最遠可射到北韓內陸地區。<br />\n分析指，日本一旦擁有長程導彈，便可能改變日美安全保障條約中「日本為盾、美國為矛」的防衞角色。日美防衞合作的指導方針曾在2015年修改，標明日本與美軍合作打擊敵人時，自衛隊必要時可支援美方，這個修改被解讀成自衞隊可以「適當形式」改變防衞角色。<br />\n中央社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181217/59039459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F59039459&d=mQqeVqlEYiUSzyOj6Sf6K7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=ab27c327\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F59039459&h=388407db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181217/59039459</a>"},{"pid":"245378c80fc61a3b8147255a2ada29e817bf1b9a","tid":944973,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3007e43aa78af3883273e608e4e7d1537b6b8110","tid":944973,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T14:45:12.000Z","msg":"日本唔發威, D港豬一直以為佢係病貓<br />\n<br />\n日本係東亞列強"},{"pid":"6eeab5f9ce6ca7677f0cf890d17ea2286f23cc97","tid":944973,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"皇軍萬歲！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18179f991a5e7f56e3a6f6c2c5e49738d61b6c6f","tid":944973,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aef61706df9af54e8bc3562dfbd343da723743be","tid":944973,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18179f991a5e7f56e3a6f6c2c5e49738d61b6c6f","tid":944973,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T16:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T22:41:27.000Z","msg":"要再侵華即係要先侵韓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d433300852d2a83a7d4b98f69e31fe8691283ee4","tid":944973,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:01:29.000Z","msg":"俄佬可能仲不滿過支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a443704f6d49cbc169c662ffefe8bb04b38c5b","tid":944973,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T23:36:05.000Z","msg":"嘩，日本得幾支飛彈仔邊夠照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快點裝備我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}